    "# haversine 함수, 거리계산\n",
    "def haversine(lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2):\n",
    "    R = 6371  # 지구 반지름 (km)\n",
    "    lat1_rad, lon1_rad, lat2_rad, lon2_rad = map(np.radians, [lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2])\n",
    "    dlat = lat2_rad - lat1_rad\n",
    "    dlon = lon2_rad - lon1_rad\n",
    "    a = np.sin(dlat / 2)**2 + np.cos(lat1_rad) * np.cos(lat2_rad) * np.sin(dlon / 2)**2\n",
    "    c = 2 * np.arctan2(np.sqrt(a), np.sqrt(1 - a))\n",
    "    return R * c\n",
    "\n",
    "# 500m 내의 유동인구수 합 계산\n",
    "results = []\n",
    "\n",
    "for _, base_row in y_df.iterrows():\n",
    "    base_id = base_row['blck_cd']\n",
    "    base_date = int(base_row['date'])\n",
    "    base_lat = base_row['lat']\n",
    "    base_lon = base_row['lon']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # df1_10에서 해당 date만 필터링\n",
    "    df1_10['STD_YM']=df1_10['STD_YM'].astype('int')\n",
    "    temp_df1_10 = df1_10[df1_10['STD_YM'] == base_date].copy()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 거리 계산 및 필터링\n",
    "    temp_df1_10['거리(km)'] = haversine(base_lat, base_lon, temp_df1_10['lat'],temp_df1_10['lon'])\n",
    "    filtered_df = temp_df1_10[temp_df1_10['거리(km)'] < 0.5]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 요일별 합계 계산\n",
    "    total_mon_pop = filtered_df['mon_pop'].sum()\n",
    "    total_tue_pop = filtered_df['tue_pop'].sum()\n",
    "    total_wed_pop = filtered_df['wed_pop'].sum()\n",
    "    total_thu_pop = filtered_df['thu_pop'].sum()\n",
    "    total_fri_pop = filtered_df['fri_pop'].sum()\n",
    "    total_sat_pop = filtered_df['sat_pop'].sum()\n",
    "    total_sun_pop = filtered_df['sun_pop'].sum()\n",
    "\n",
    "    temp_results = {\n",
    "        'blck_cd': base_id,\n",
    "        'date': str(base_date),\n",
    "        'mon_pop': total_mon_pop,\n",
    "        'tue_pop': total_tue_pop,\n",
    "        'wed_pop': total_wed_pop,\n",
    "        'thu_pop': total_thu_pop,\n",
    "        'fri_pop': total_fri_pop,\n",
    "        'sat_pop': total_sat_pop,\n",
    "        'sun_pop': total_sun_pop\n",
    "    }\n",
    "    results.append(temp_results)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 결과 확인\n",
    "df_results = pd.DataFrame(results)\n",
    "df_results"

    "# 모델 평가 함수\n",
    "def evaluate_model(model, X_train, y_train, X_test, y_test):\n",
    "    model.fit(X_train, y_train)\n",
    "    y_pred = model.predict(X_test)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    mse = mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred)\n",
    "    rmse = np.sqrt(mse)\n",
    "    mae = mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred)\n",
    "    r2 = r2_score(y_test, y_pred)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return {\"MSE\": mse, \"RMSE\": rmse, \"MAE\": mae, \"R²\": r2}\n",
    "\n",
    "# 결과 출력\n",
    "def print_results(model_name, results):\n",
    "    print(f\"Model: {model_name}\")\n",
    "    for metric, value in results.items():\n",
    "        print(f\"{metric}: {value:.4f}\")\n",
    "    print(\"-\" * 30)"
   ]

    "# 러닝커브(R_square)\n",
    "def plot_learning_curve(model, X_train, y_train, model_name):\n",
    "    train_sizes, train_scores, valid_scores = learning_curve(\n",
    "        model, X_train, y_train, cv=5, train_sizes=np.linspace(0.1, 1.0, 10), n_jobs=-1\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 학습 점수와 검증 점수의 평균 및 표준편차 계산\n",
    "    train_mean = np.mean(train_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "    train_std = np.std(train_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "    valid_mean = np.mean(valid_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "    valid_std = np.std(valid_scores, axis=1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 학습 곡선 그리기\n",
    "    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "    plt.plot(train_sizes, train_mean, label=\"Training score\", color=\"blue\")\n",
    "    plt.plot(train_sizes, valid_mean, label=\"Validation score\", color=\"green\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 신뢰 구간을 표시하기 위해 면적을 채움\n",
    "    plt.fill_between(train_sizes, train_mean - train_std, train_mean + train_std, alpha=0.2, color=\"blue\")\n",
    "    plt.fill_between(train_sizes, valid_mean - valid_std, valid_mean + valid_std, alpha=0.2, color=\"green\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.title(f\"Learning Curve: {model_name}\")\n",
    "    plt.xlabel(\"Training Size\")\n",
    "    plt.ylabel(\"Score (R²)\")\n",
    "    plt.legend()\n",
    "    plt.grid(True)\n",
    "    plt.show()\n",

    "# GeoDataFrame으로 변환\n",
    "df_result = gpd.GeoDataFrame(df_result, geometry=df_result['centroid'])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Geometry에서 위도(latitude)와 경도(longitude) 추출\n",
    "df_result['longitude'] = df_result.geometry.x\n",
    "df_result['latitude'] = df_result.geometry.y\n",
    "\n",
    "# Haversine 함수\n",
    "def haversine(lat1, lon1, lat2, lon2):\n",
    "    R = 6371000  # 지구 반지름 (미터)\n",
    "    phi1, phi2 = np.radians(lat1), np.radians(lat2)\n",
    "    dphi = np.radians(lat2 - lat1)\n",
    "    dlambda = np.radians(lon2 - lon1)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    a = np.sin(dphi / 2)**2 + np.cos(phi1) * np.cos(phi2) * np.sin(dlambda / 2)**2\n",
    "    c = 2 * np.arctan2(np.sqrt(a), np.sqrt(1 - a))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    return R * c\n",
    "\n",
    "# df2_4가 일반 DataFrame인지 확인하고 처리\n",
    "if 'geometry' not in df2_4.columns:\n",
    "    df2_4['geometry'] = [Point(lon, lat) for lon, lat in zip(df2_4['lon'], df2_4['lat'])]\n",
    "df2_4 = gpd.GeoDataFrame(df2_4, geometry='geometry')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 500m 반경 내 상권 개수 계산\n",
    "def count_pois_within_radius_haversine(val_row, df2_4, radius=500):\n",
    "    val_lat, val_lon = val_row['latitude'], val_row['longitude']\n",
    "    distances = haversine(\n",
    "        val_lat, val_lon,\n",
    "        df2_4['lat'].values, df2_4['lon'].values\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    return np.sum(distances <= radius)\n",
    "\n",
    "df_result['com_cnt'] = df_result.apply(lambda row: count_pois_within_radius_haversine(row, df2_4), axis=1)\n",
    "df_result"
   ]

    "# 500m 반경 내 버스 정류장 개수 계산 함수\n",
    "def count_bus_stops_within_radius(val_row, df2_5, radius=500):\n",
    "    val_lat, val_lon = val_row['latitude'], val_row['longitude']\n",
    "    distances = haversine(\n",
    "        val_lat, val_lon,\n",
    "        df2_5['lat'].values, df2_5['lon'].values\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    return np.sum(distances <= radius)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 500m 반경 내 버스 정류장 개수 계산\n",
    "df_result['bus_stop_cnt'] = df_result.apply(lambda row: count_bus_stops_within_radius(row, df2_5), axis=1)\n",
    "df_result"

    "# 500m 반경 내 평균 인구 수 계산 함수\n",
    "def calculate_average_population(val_row, df2_10, radius=500):\n",
    "    val_lat, val_lon = val_row['latitude'], val_row['longitude']\n",
    "    distances = haversine(\n",
    "        val_lat, val_lon,\n",
    "        df2_10['lat'].values, df2_10['lon'].values\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    within_radius = distances <= radius\n",
    "    if np.sum(within_radius) > 0:\n",
    "        # 반경 내 데이터가 있으면 월~일 평균 계산\n",
    "        weekly_avg = df2_10.loc[within_radius, ['mon_pop', 'tue_pop', 'wed_pop', 'thu_pop', 'fri_pop', 'sat_pop', 'sun_pop']].mean(axis=1).mean()\n",
    "        return weekly_avg\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        # 반경 내 데이터가 없으면 NaN 반환\n",
    "        return np.nan\n",
    "\n",
    "# val_df에 월~일 평균 인구 수 칼럼 추가\n",
    "df_result['day_pop'] = df_result.apply(lambda row: calculate_average_population(row, df2_10), axis=1)\n",
    "df_result"
   ]
